# Regression test for set_param on ConstantExpression parameters.
# Mimics T1 polynomial model: d = d__FREE (ConstantExpression).
# Bug: set_param("d", 27) was silently overwritten by re-evaluation.
# After fix: set_param("d", 27) detaches expression, d stays at 27.
begin parameters
    1 d__FREE    70.0  # Constant
    2 d          d__FREE  # ConstantExpression
    3 _rateLaw1  1  # Constant
end parameters
begin species
    1 counter() 0
end species
begin reactions
    1 0 1 _rateLaw1 #_R1
end reactions
begin groups
    1 x  1
end groups
